 311:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 312:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** * \brief
 313:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  Performs full data processing of all enabled widgets.
 314:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 315:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** * \details
 316:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  This function performs all data processes for all enabled widgets in the
 317:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  Component. The following tasks are executed as part of processing all the
ARM GAS  C:\Users\ash750\AppData\Local\Temp\ccUWbBEQ.s 			page 11


 318:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  widgets:
 319:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *    1. Apply raw count filters to the raw counts, if they are enabled in the
 320:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *       customizer.
 321:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *    2. Update the thresholds if the SmartSense Full Auto-Tuning is enabled in
 322:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *       the customizer.
 323:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *    3. Update the baselines and difference counts for all the sensors.
 324:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *    4. Update the sensor and widget status (on/off), update the centroid for
 325:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *       the sliders and the X/Y position for the touchpads.
 326:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 327:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  This function is called by an application program only after all the enabled
 328:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  widgets (and sensors) in the Component is scanned. Calling this function
 329:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  multiple times without sensor scanning causes unexpected behavior.
 330:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 331:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  The disabled widgets are not processed by this function. To disable/enable
 332:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  a widget, set the appropriate values in the
 333:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  CapSense_WDGT_ENABLE<RegisterNumber>_PARAM_ID register using the
 334:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  CapSense_SetParam() function.
 335:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 336:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  If the Ballistic multiplier filter is enabled the Timestamp must be
 337:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  updated before calling this function using the
 338:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  CapSense_IncrementGestureTimestamp() function.
 339:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 340:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  If the Self-test library is enabled, this function executes the baseline duplication
 341:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  test. Refer to CapSense_CheckBaselineDuplication() for details.
 342:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 343:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  If the ballistic multiplier filter is enabled, make sure the timestamp is
 344:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  updated before calling this function. Use one of the following functions to update
 345:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  the timestamp:
 346:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  - CapSense_IncrementGestureTimestamp().
 347:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  - CapSense_SetGestureTimestamp().
 348:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 349:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** * \return
 350:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  Returns the status of the processing operation. If CYRET_SUCCESS is not received,
 351:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  the processing fails and retries may be required.
 352:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 353:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *******************************************************************************/
