 411:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 412:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** * \brief
 413:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  Performs full data processing of the specified widget if it is enabled.
 414:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 415:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** * \details
 416:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  This function performs exactly the same tasks as
 417:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  CapSense_ProcessAllWidgets(), but only for a specified widget. This
 418:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  function can be used along with the CapSense_SetupWidget() and
 419:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  CapSense_Scan() functions to scan and process data for a specific
 420:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  widget. This function is called only after all the sensors in the
 421:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  widgets are scanned. A disabled widget is not processed by this function.
 422:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 423:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  A pipeline scan method (i.e. during scanning of a widget perform processing
 424:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  of the previously scanned widget) can be implemented using this function and
 425:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  it may reduce the total execution time, increase the refresh rate and
 426:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  decrease the average power consumption.
 427:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 428:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  If the Ballistic multiplier filter is enabled the Timestamp must be
 429:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  updated before calling this function using the
 430:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  CapSense_IncrementGestureTimestamp() function.
 431:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 432:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  If the Self-test library is enabled, this function executes the baseline duplication
 433:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  test. Refer to CapSense_CheckBaselineDuplication() for details.
 434:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 435:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  If the specified widget has enabled ballistic multiplier filter, make sure
 436:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  the timestamp is updated before calling this function. Use one of the following
 437:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  functions to update the timestamp:
 438:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  - CapSense_IncrementGestureTimestamp().
 439:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  - CapSense_SetGestureTimestamp().
 440:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 441:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** * \param widgetId
 442:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  Specifies the ID number of the widget to be processed.
 443:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  A macro for the widget ID can be found in the
 444:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  CapSense Configuration header file defined as
 445:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  CapSense_<WidgetName>_WDGT_ID
 446:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
 447:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** * \return
 448:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  Returns the status of the widget processing:
 449:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  - CYRET_SUCCESS - The operation is successfully completed.
ARM GAS  C:\Users\ash750\AppData\Local\Temp\ccUWbBEQ.s 			page 15


 450:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  - CYRET_BAD_PARAM - The input parameter is invalid.
 451:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  - CYRET_INVALID_STATE - The specified widget is disabled.
 452:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *  - CYRET_BAD_DATA - The processing is failed.
 453:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_Control.c **** *
